name: osm2hydro
short_description:
Read the Documentation for more information. osm2hydro is part of the Deltares OpenEarth initiative

Browse sources, checkout and see examples in examples/ directory - use IPython Notebook or run using scripts.

Working version trunk
Version 0.9
Reference
If you use osm2hydro please refer to the paper describing the tool:

Schellekens, J., Brolsma, R.J., Dahm, R.J., Donchyts, G.V., Winsemius, H.C., 2014. Rapid setup of hydrological and hydraulic models using OpenStreetMap? and the SRTM derived digital elevation model. Environmental Modelling & Software 61, 98–105. doi:10.1016/j.envsoft.2014.07.006
summary: osm2hydro uses openstreetmap to setup hydrological/hydraulic models
